title: Baked Almond Tart | Jamie’s Italian UNSEEN
description:
We’re taking you back in time to when Jamie celebrated turning 30 with a road trip through Italy. Here he is in Lazio where a stay with the local monks ended in him having to cater for an extremely important guest. But were his cherry and peach tarts with frangipane filling inspired?  Jamie can only pray for a miracle.

If you like seeing a baby faced Jamie let us know and we'll dig out some more never-seen-before crackers to share with you.
What's your favourite Italian food? Leave your comments in the box below, we love to hear them!
